divs: Sighting DetailsMY DAUGHTER EMAILED ME THESE PHOTOS SHE TOOK WITH HER CELL PHONE. THEY WERE RIDING DOWN COUNTY Y BETWEEN PESTIGO AND OCONTO. THAY LOOKED IN A FIELD AND SAW LIGHTS ON THE OBJECT IN THE BACK OF THE FIELD. IT WAS RIGHT OF ABOVE THE TREE LINE IT MADE NO SOUND AND DID NOT MOVE. THEY LOCKED THE DOORS ROLLED DOWN THE WINDOW TO TAKE PICTURES AND LEFT. THEY WERE AFRAID AND CAME DIRCTLY HOME. IT WAS ABOUT 300 FT LONG.
